# ============================================
# HOW TO GET THESE KEYS:
# ============================================
# 
# YouTube API:
# 1. Go to https://console.cloud.google.com
# 2. Create project "CredX Social"
# 3. Enable YouTube Data API v3
# 4. Create OAuth 2.0 credentials
# 5. Download client_secret.json
# 6. Run: node scripts/youtube-auth.js
# 7. Copy refresh_token to this file
#
# Instagram API:
# 1. Go to https://developers.facebook.com
# 2. Create app "CredX Content"
# 3. Add Instagram Graph API product
# 4. Get User Access Token
# 5. Convert to Long-Lived Token
# 6. Connect Instagram Business account
#
# HeyGen API:
# 1. Go to https://www.heygen.com
# 2. Create account
# 3. Go to API section
# 4. Copy API Key
#
# OpenAI API:
# 1. Go to https://platform.openai.com
# 2. Create account
# 3. Go to API Keys
# 4. Create new secret key
# ============================================
